      i0.ɵɵelementStart(70, "h2", 48);
      i0.ɵɵtext(71, " About Us ");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(72, "p", 49);
      i0.ɵɵtext(73, " Welcome to Jarek Farms, a Nigerian-registered company with a mission to improve essential food supplies for the people of Nigeria and to create employment and training opportunities for Nigerians. Our visionary group of Nigerian and UK nationals is committed to making a positive impact in Nigeria's agricultural sector. We have successfully launched our poultry business, and we are now expanding organically into other areas of agricultural need in Nigeria. Our goal is to help reduce national shortages of essential food products. ");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(74, "p", 50);
      i0.ɵɵtext(75, " At Jarek Farms, we believe in sustainable agriculture that benefits both the environment and the local community. Our operations are designed to create employment and training opportunities for Nigerians, thereby supporting the country's economic growth. We are committed to excellence in all aspects of our business, from production to distribution. Our goal is to be a leading supplier of quality agricultural products in Nigeria and beyond. Join us on this journey towards a brighter future for Nigeria's agricultural sector. ");
