      i0.ɵɵelementStart(82, "dd", 56);
      i0.ɵɵtext(83, " At Jarek Farms, we understand the importance of grains in Nigeria's food supply. That's why we're committed to increasing production and distribution of various grains, including maize, rice, and wheat. As a leading supplier, we provide grains for both human consumption and animal feed. ");
