      i0.ɵɵelementStart(94, "dd", 56);
      i0.ɵɵtext(95, " At Jarek Farms, we are proud to offer a diverse range of chicken products to meet the needs of our customers. Whether you prefer frozen or live chickens, we've got you covered. Our chickens are raised under strict conditions to ensure their health and well-being, resulting in delicious, high-quality meat. ");
