      i0.ɵɵelementStart(100, "dd", 56);
      i0.ɵɵtext(101, " At Jarek Farms, we understand the importance of eggs as a nutritious and versatile food source. That's why we are dedicated to providing high-quality, fresh eggs to our customers in Nigeria. Our eggs are carefully handled and packaged in crates to ensure their freshness and integrity. ");
