      i0.ɵɵelementStart(106, "dd", 56);
      i0.ɵɵtext(107, " At Jarek Farms, we are committed to providing a range of turkey products to meet the diverse needs of our customers. Whether you prefer frozen or live turkeys, we have you covered. Our turkeys are raised under strict conditions to ensure their health and well-being, resulting in delicious, high-quality meat. ");
